node.text:
HIGH STATUS SUMMIT 2020. This photo was taken late January 2020, about a month before the lockdowns started. I announced before this event it would be my last High-Status Summit. Why? Because these things are a lot of work. Getting 800-1,000 people to a venue for 3 days and putting on an electrifying experience for them is no joke. HOWEVER… with that said, now that it’s been 18 months, I have been getting the itch a little bit to do another big event like this one. What do you think? Should I? Would you come? LMK what you think in the comments section. 

P.S. Do you like Instagram? My team and I are looking for a few more ppl who want to earn a full-time income from home just typing messages on social media. If you’re interested, message me the word “Side hustle”. Thanks!
